name: R5-CareTeam-R4-CareTeam
title: Concept map to convert a FHIR R5 CareTeam into FHIR R4

element.display: Planned participants in the coordination and delivery of care

target.display: Planned participants in the coordination and delivery of care for a patient or group
target.comment: R5 `CareTeam` maps as Equivalent to R4 `CareTeam`
R5 `CareTeam.category` maps as Equivalent to R4 `CareTeam.category`
R5 `CareTeam.contained` maps as Equivalent to R4 `CareTeam.contained`

R5 `CareTeam.extension` maps as SourceIsBroaderThanTarget to R4 `CareTeam.extension` - extension has change due to type change: R5 `extension` `Extension` maps as SourceIsBroaderThanTarget for R4 `extension`
R5 `CareTeam.id` maps as Equivalent to R4 `CareTeam.id`
R5 `CareTeam.identifier` maps as Equivalent to R4 `CareTeam.identifier`

element.display: A set of rules under which this content was created

target.display: A set of rules under which this content was created
target.comment: R5 `CareTeam.implicitRules` maps as Equivalent to R4 `CareTeam.implicitRules`

R5 `CareTeam.language` maps as SourceIsNarrowerThanTarget to R4 `CareTeam.language` - language changed the binding strength from Required to Preferred; language has change due to type change: R5 `language` `code` maps as SourceIsNarrowerThanTarget for R4 `language`

element.display: Organization responsible for the care team

target.display: Organization responsible for the care team
target.comment: R5 `CareTeam.managingOrganization` maps as Equivalent to R4 `CareTeam.managingOrganization`
R5 `CareTeam.meta` maps as Equivalent to R4 `CareTeam.meta`

R5 `CareTeam.modifierExtension` maps as SourceIsBroaderThanTarget to R4 `CareTeam.modifierExtension` - modifierExtension has change due to type change: R5 `modifierExtension` `Extension` maps as SourceIsBroaderThanTarget for R4 `modifierExtension`

element.display: Name of the team, such as crisis assessment team

target.display: Name of the team, such as crisis assessment team
target.comment: R5 `CareTeam.name` maps as Equivalent to R4 `CareTeam.name`
R5 `CareTeam.note` maps as SourceIsBroaderThanTarget to R4 `CareTeam.note` - note has change due to type change: R5 `note` `Annotation` maps as SourceIsBroaderThanTarget for R4 `note`
R5 `CareTeam.participant` maps as Equivalent to R4 `CareTeam.participant`

R5 `CareTeam.participant.coverage[x]` maps as SourceIsBroaderThanTarget to R4 `CareTeam.participant.period` - period has change due to type change: R5 coverage[x] Timing has no equivalent or mapped type in R4 period

R5 `CareTeam.participant.extension` maps as SourceIsBroaderThanTarget to R4 `CareTeam.participant.extension` - extension has change due to type change: R5 `extension` `Extension` maps as SourceIsBroaderThanTarget for R4 `extension`
R5 `CareTeam.participant.id` maps as Equivalent to R4 `CareTeam.participant.id`
R5 `CareTeam.participant.member` maps as Equivalent to R4 `CareTeam.participant.member`

element.display: Extensions that cannot be ignored even if unrecognized

target.display: Extensions that cannot be ignored even if unrecognized
target.comment: R5 `CareTeam.participant.modifierExtension` maps as SourceIsBroaderThanTarget to R4 `CareTeam.participant.modifierExtension` - modifierExtension has change due to type change: R5 `modifierExtension` `Extension` maps as SourceIsBroaderThanTarget for R4 `modifierExtension`
R5 `CareTeam.participant.onBehalfOf` maps as Equivalent to R4 `CareTeam.participant.onBehalfOf`
R5 `CareTeam.participant.role` maps as SourceIsNarrowerThanTarget to R4 `CareTeam.participant.role` - role changed from scalar to array (max cardinality from 1 to *)
R5 `CareTeam.period` maps as Equivalent to R4 `CareTeam.period`

R5 `CareTeam.reason` maps as SourceIsBroaderThanTarget to R4 `CareTeam.reasonCode` - reasonCode has change due to type change: R5 reason CodeableReference has no equivalent or mapped type in R4 reasonCode

R5 `CareTeam.reason` maps as RelatedTo to R4 `CareTeam.reasonReference` - reasonReference removed a binding requirement - Example http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/clinical-findings; reasonReference has change due to type change: R5 reason CodeableReference has no equivalent or mapped type in R4 reasonReference

R5 `CareTeam.status` maps as Equivalent to R4 `CareTeam.status` - status has compatible required binding for code type: http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/care-team-status|5.0.0 and http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/care-team-status|4.0.1 (Equivalent)
R5 `CareTeam.subject` maps as Equivalent to R4 `CareTeam.subject`

element.display: A contact detail for the care team (that applies to all members)

target.display: A contact detail for the care team (that applies to all members)
target.comment: R5 `CareTeam.telecom` maps as Equivalent to R4 `CareTeam.telecom`

element.display: Text summary of the resource, for human interpretation

target.display: Text summary of the resource, for human interpretation
target.comment: R5 `CareTeam.text` maps as Equivalent to R4 `CareTeam.text`
